dct_description_sm: This collection contains the GIS data used in the analysis and in making the maps.
These layers were downloaded from the Lincoln Institute website (http://www.lincolninst.edu/subcenters/atlas-urban-expansion/gis-data.aspx) in May 2015.
System requirements: Geographic Information Systems (GIS) software that reads shapefile and raster formats.
